WEBVTT

00:02.429 --> 00:03.629
James.

00:03.703 --> 00:04.981
James! No.

00:04.983 --> 00:07.141
No-one else
is to know about this.

00:07.143 --> 00:08.381
No-one.

00:08.383 --> 00:10.101
I'd only share what I know
for his wellbeing.

00:10.103 --> 00:13.381
Good. Then there will be no need
for you to break the confidence.

00:13.383 --> 00:15.903
I know a disappointed man
when I see one.

00:17.023 --> 00:18.823
We're going to have a baby, James.

00:19.343 --> 00:20.581
But this...

00:20.583 --> 00:22.941
This will make a difference.

00:22.943 --> 00:25.421
You seemed very taken with
the singer yesterday.

00:25.423 --> 00:29.703
To them, he's just a farmer,
and I'd be just a fool.

00:29.742 --> 00:31.100
Our rooms have locks.

00:31.102 --> 00:32.299
I want the key to mine.

00:32.302 --> 00:35.180
In my experience,
one doesn't guard a door

00:35.182 --> 00:37.302
unless there's
something in the room.

00:39.142 --> 00:43.300
You checked the references
of a woman called Sarah Adams.

00:43.302 --> 00:45.180
That is not her real name.

00:45.182 --> 00:47.060
I'll get to the bottom of it,
Elizabeth.

00:47.062 --> 00:48.980
Because it is high time we knew

00:48.982 --> 00:52.422
exactly who Miss Bridget Adams
really is.

